    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“Lonely street artist Gene takes the desperate step of joining a crew of fellow graffiti rebels led by the cunning and arrogant young Vanessa. With his help, will the gang be able to shake up the society of their hometown, which is suffocating under the cruelty of the authorities and the regime?”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VIOLE[n]T RUSH</strong> is a short visual novel that will captivate you for a couple of hours with its intricate plot and cyberpunk atmosphere. Learn about the street art movement in the futuristic metropolis of New Astra, the past of its greatest crew – HE11AHOUND – and its legendary founders. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Inside you’ll find:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An engaging, fast-paced story, 2-3 hours long;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stylized, hand-drawn graphics;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Strong, vivid characters;</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Cinematic sound effects, an atmospheric soundtrack, and vibrant visuals.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game uses licensed Creative Commons music made by the following artists: <strong>Beat Mekanik, bent wyre, BrokeMC, Kellee Maize, Lightning Traveler, Pierce Murphy</strong>, and <strong>Yshwa.</strong></i></p>",
